// Card
// Styled container with optional title, subtitle, footer, collapsible toggle, and elevation shadow.
// Returns nothing if hidden is true.

FUNCTION getElevationClasses(elevation) -> string
  Maps elevation level (1–5) to Tailwind shadow classes (shadow-sm through shadow-xl).

---

FUNCTION Card(props) -> ReactNode                                         EXPORT
  Renders a rounded bordered container.
  IF title or subtitle is provided, renders a header section with them.
  IF collapsible is true, adds a toggle button in the header that shows/hides the content body.
  IF footer is provided and content is not collapsed, renders a footer strip below the content.
  Applies custom border/background colors via inline styles when provided.
  Returns null if hidden is true.
